							&lt;img src=&quot;http://adwxview.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/TB2s0jdhrBmpuFjSZFuXXaG_XXa_!!276530134.jpg&quot; /&gt; &lt;span&gt;今非昔比&lt;/span&gt; 
